  ('social-worker-moex-02151', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當我們要判斷兩個變項間是否有因果關係時，下列那種判斷標準不合適？', '["兩個變項有相關，就有因果關係", "兩變項間關係不是由於第三變項造成", "在時間順序上，被視為原因的變項必須先於被視為結果的變項", "兩個變項之間須互為共變"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "88073911b247", "answer_pdf_sha1": "449337010204", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02152', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於演繹法的說明，何者有誤？', '["演繹法從假設的擬定開始", "是種從理論到研究的過程", "與歸納法奠基於相同的哲學觀", "實驗方法與調查方法是立基於演繹法"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "88073911b247", "answer_pdf_sha1": "449337010204", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02153', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當資料呈現正偏態（positively skewed）時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["平均數可能小於眾數", "中位數可能大於平均數", "中位數可能趨近於平均數", "大部分的分數分布在橫軸數值較低位置"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "88073911b247", "answer_pdf_sha1": "449337010204", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
